Hugging Face model assets
-------------------------

Full local model mode downloads these model files during explicit setup:

- model repository: `onnx-community/tanaos-emotion-detection-v1-ONNX`
- source: https://huggingface.co/onnx-community/tanaos-emotion-detection-v1-ONNX
- license shown by the Hugging Face model page/API on 2026-06-21: MIT
- task: `text-classification`
- selected ONNX file: `onnx/model_int8.onnx`
- tokenizer/config files:
  - `config.json`
  - `special_tokens_map.json`
  - `tokenizer.json`
  - `tokenizer_config.json`

These model files are not committed to Git. They are downloaded into the
ignored `models/` directory by `npm run setup-model` and verified by expected
size and SHA-256 hash before full local model mode is treated as ready.

ONNX Runtime Web local runtime files
------------------------------------

Full local model mode also copies ONNX Runtime Web runtime files into the
ignored `runtime/onnxruntime/` directory during `npm run setup-model`.

Those copied runtime files come from the installed `onnxruntime-web` package
and remain under the upstream `onnxruntime-web` license.

